723154f-a.title: Manhattan: St. Nicholas Avenue - 167th Street (West)
723154f-a.text:
1154 to 114O St. Nicholas Ave., east side, south from West 168th to
West 167th Streets, showing the 2-story Washington Heights Building
(Nos. 1154-1148). Also shown (left) are Nos. 564 to 550 West 168th Street,
south side, east from St. Nicholas to Audubon Aves. This area is known
as Mitchell Square.
June 15, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
